Within the Ark, she stayed near Teletran 1. Curious as she started to tinker 
with a few things. Every so often would be searching for a few things. 

But, every so often as she moved about, she caught the glimpes of the dormant 
Megatron. Each time was a twist to her fuel pump. Or was it stomach? In this 
type of a body, she was unfamiliar with it's needs or terms or functions. 

She continued on with her business. 

--part1_3e.2fa9d90c.2bf5b448_boundary
